reviewText: Sadler at his best.  The story line isn't for everyone but for those that served in a position such as the 'main' character did should be able to enjoy this very much.  (Old memories abound!)

As a retired Maine, I found some fault.  For example, A Marine would never wear a gold eagle globe and anchor on a green cover.  The story line was a little hard to follow at the beginning but it is an okay movie for entertainment value.
